Class Entity

java.lang.Object
Entity
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bullet, Enemy, Player
public class Entity extends Object
Base class for all in-game entities such as Player, Enemy, and Bullet.

Stores shared attributes including position, velocity, health, and physics behaviour such as jumping, gravity, and collision detection.

psyjr14
